      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SECRET FENKEL (4) stuck on well last start to finish third over 1950m at Ipswich after showing good early speed. Placed to advantage so expect another forward showing from the favourable draw. DONATELLO (2) hasn't been far away lately including a last-start fourth over 1550m at Randwick Kensington. Extra trip a plus and rates among the main hopes. SHARK PARK (8) was in contention on the corner and ran a better race last start to finish a close second over 1900m at Gold Coast Poly after missing the placings at the previous appearance. Looks well placed so expect another big run. LUMINIZED (3) was allowed to drift back from an outside draw last time but found the line strongly to finish fifth, beaten 2.25 lengths, over 1950m at Ipswich. Warrants plenty of respect.",
